rules.searchText:
.&#39;&#39;Connor:&#39;&#39; //Anyway. Even if this has been a costly endeavor for you, I hope you&#39;ll grant me one last favor, Mr. $pcLastName. That is to absolve my family&#39;s status as slaves. Allow them to live here as your servants; as free citizens of Ikaanos. You have that power. I know they got into this mess because of what I did. I&#39;ll repay you with my undying loyalty.//
&lt;&lt;set $take to 1&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;/if&gt;&gt;


&lt;&lt;if $adpos is 1&gt;&gt;
&#39;&#39;You:&#39;&#39; //I&#39;m sorry, Connor, but that will not happen. I don’t intend to keep them as hostages but they&#39;re still my property – freeing them would make me look weak. They remain here, bound to house $pcLastName as indentured servants.//
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&#39;&#39;Connor:&#39;&#39; //(Long silence) I see. I guess I misunderstood how this would play out. Guess it&#39;s fair, in a way. I will not allow you to hurt or abuse them in any way, however. Consider that as a… friendly warning.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Celeste. Darling. Come, I&#39;ll show you to your new quarters.
//
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Celeste&#39;s and Erica&#39;s &#39;&#39;WILLPOWER (-10)&#39;&#39; have decreased!

&lt;&lt;for _sund range $npc&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;if _sund.girlid is 218 or _sund.girlid is 217&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;set _sund.willpower-=10&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;/if&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;/for&gt;&gt;

&lt;&lt;/if&gt;&gt;


&lt;&lt;if $adpos is 2&gt;&gt;
&#39;&#39;You:&#39;&#39; //Please, Connor. You don’t have to ask me. 
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
I, $pcFirstName $pcLastName, hereby declare Celeste Sunderland and Erica Sunderland as freeborns - by the power invested in me by the state of Ikaanos and house Kymanto. They are from this moment fully absolved from indentured servanthood. //
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Connor gives you a gratifying smile.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&#39;&#39;Connor:&#39;&#39; //The words of a true Master of Ikaanos. Thank you.//
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&#39;&#39;Erica Sunderland:&#39;&#39; //Oh honey (sobbing). Now everything is like it was before. Thank you, Mr. $pcLastName. Thank you for rescuing us.//
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Connor&#39;s &#39;&#39;Happiness (+10), Affection (+20)&#39;&#39; and &#39;&#39;Respect (+10)&#39;&#39; toward you have increased!
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;blink_me&quot;&gt;&#39;&#39;New trait gained (Connor):&#39;&#39; Undying loyalty.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&#39;&#39;New status (Celeste, Erica):&#39;&#39; Servant.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Celeste&#39;s and Erica&#39;s &#39;&#39;WILLPOWER (+5)&#39;&#39; has increased!

&lt;&lt;for _sund range $npc&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;if _sund.girlid is 218 or _sund.girlid is 217&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;set _sund.willpower+=5&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;set _sund.status to 3&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;/if&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;/for&gt;&gt;

&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;&lt;include MissionComp&gt;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;&lt;set $npc.av23.happiness+=10&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;set $npc.av23.masterlove+=20&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;set $npc.av23.respect+=10&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;set $npc.av23.traitloyal=100&gt;&gt;

